biome.tes.ascadian_isles_desc: The Ascadian Isles are the lush, fertile, green lowlands on the south-southwestern corner of Vvardenfell. Settlements include Vivec City, Ebonheart, Suran and Pelagiad. The large Daedric ruins of Ald Sotha lie to the east of Vivec. Most of Vvardenfell's farms and plantations are in this region. These typically include Netch herding and agriculture. Marshmerrow is an important crop in this region. Slavery is common in this area, especially on the plantations and manor houses.
